#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: mixed known and unknown tags with a schema active. Known tags
# (_cell.*) are routed to structured tables. Unknown tags (_my_custom.*,
# _another_unknown, _quoted_number) are not in cif_core, so they must fall through
# to _cif_fallback even when a schema is present. Neither routing must lose data.
# Dictionary: cif_core

data_test_unknown_tag
_cell.length_a    4.500
_cell.length_b    4.500
_cell.length_c    9.000
_cell.angle_alpha 90
_cell.angle_beta  90
_cell.angle_gamma 90
_my_custom.property   hello
_my_custom.number     42
_another_unknown      world
_quoted_number        "37.4(2)"
